inputSpec.help:
Which chr/fragment. Chromosome name must be the same as in reference sequence and in read file. Default (ALL) will loop over all chromosomes. The search for indels and SVs can also be limited to a specific region;
 20:10,000,000 will only look for indels and SVs after position 10,000,000 == [10M, end] 
-c 20:5,000,000-15,000,000 will report indels in the range between and including the bases at position 5,000,000 and 15,000,000 = [5M, 15M]
